taiwan 1986 balanc of payment surplu is record taiwan 's balanc of payment surplu widen to a record 16.62 billion u.s. dlr in calendar 1986 from 9.35 billion in 1985 , the central bank said . a bank offici attribut the increas mainli to taiwan' grow trade surplu , which increas to a record 16.8 billion u.s. dlr in 1986 from 11.2 billion in 1985. he said the deficit on invis trade narrow to 740 mln u.s. dlr from 1.97 billion . invis earn rose to 6.77 billion from 5.09 billion while invis spend climb to 7.51 billion from 7.06 billion , he said .